### Searching API Status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/searching/status

### POST a cache record for a key
POST http://localhost:3000/api/searching/add/ HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "name":"John", 
    "role": "user", 
    "dob": "2025-01-01"
}


### Searching API Search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/searching/search/user


### Delete a cache record for a key
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/searching/delete/34c6f47d-f5c0-4ed4-b209-43d1500a5eee

